https://github.com/pagehelper/Mybatis-PageHelper/commit/c1d2134088fc63ee7c4e2d6a2069190a6555abfc

PAGEPARAMETER_SECOND始终是int类型，而不是long类型。
正确的应该是
```
            if (page.getStartRow() == 0) {
                //newParameterMappings.add(new ParameterMapping.Builder(ms.getConfiguration(), PAGEPARAMETER_SECOND, long.class).build());
                newParameterMappings.add(new ParameterMapping.Builder(ms.getConfiguration(), PAGEPARAMETER_SECOND, int.class).build());
            } else {
                newParameterMappings.add(new ParameterMapping.Builder(ms.getConfiguration(), PAGEPARAMETER_FIRST, long.class).build());
                newParameterMappings.add(new ParameterMapping.Builder(ms.getConfiguration(), PAGEPARAMETER_SECOND, int.class).build());
            }
```

@abel533 将long修改为int，使代码能够运行后，#529 的问题仍在存在。

将ExecutorUtil的第166行后，增加一行调试代码
https://github.com/pagehelper/Mybatis-PageHelper/blob/d323b6087da9db97ca24191e80e76eb483b854d4/src/main/java/com/github/pagehelper/util/ExecutorUtil.java#L166
```
    public static <E> List<E> pageQuery(Dialect dialect, Executor executor, MappedStatement ms, Object parameter,
                                        RowBounds rowBounds, ResultHandler resultHandler,
                                        BoundSql boundSql, CacheKey cacheKey) throws SQLException {
        //判断是否需要进行分页查询
        if (dialect.beforePage(ms, parameter, rowBounds)) {
            //生成分页的缓存 key
            CacheKey pageKey = cacheKey;
            //处理参数对象
            parameter = dialect.processParameterObject(ms, parameter, boundSql, pageKey);
            BoundSql sqlTest = ms.getBoundSql(parameter);

            //调用方言获取分页 sql
            String pageSql = dialect.getPageSql(ms, boundSql, parameter, rowBounds, pageKey);
            BoundSql pageBoundSql = new BoundSql(ms.getConfiguration(), pageSql, boundSql.getParameterMappings(), parameter);
```

sqlTest.getSql()的值为"select * from user where name like '%null'"，因为`Page<User> selectSimple(String str);`传入了str=null

